WEBVTT

00:12.012 --> 00:14.347
Come back, Se-ah! Se-ah!

00:15.849 --> 00:17.267
I'm right here. Come back.

00:18.393 --> 00:20.061
Stop it, Na-ri!

00:20.145 --> 00:22.230
If Se-ah doesn't make it,
I'm gonna kill you myself!

00:26.443 --> 00:27.485
Se-ah!

00:34.868 --> 00:35.702
Hey!

00:48.882 --> 00:49.924
HA-YOUNG

00:56.681 --> 00:58.683
Geon-woo. It's Ha-joon's sister.

00:58.767 --> 01:01.519
I'm sending you my location.
Bring Se-ah here now!

01:02.228 --> 01:03.646
Geon-woo, no.

01:05.023 --> 01:07.150
-Se-ah. Se-ah!
-You can't.

01:08.651 --> 01:09.611
Don't listen to her.

01:10.570 --> 01:12.280
-It's not real.
-Geon-woo, are you there?

01:12.363 --> 01:14.783
It's all bogus. Just like before.

01:14.866 --> 01:15.784
Hang up.

01:16.868 --> 01:20.538
I'll float a lantern up over the
compound but you need to get moving.

01:20.622 --> 01:23.291
That's not Haetsal. You can't listen.

01:23.875 --> 01:24.918
Turn it off.

01:25.460 --> 01:27.003
You need to do as I say!

01:27.087 --> 01:28.421
It's the demon.

01:29.839 --> 01:32.550
Se-ah's life is in your hands!
You have to trust me.

01:36.137 --> 01:40.266
You need to bring Se-ah
here now! This is real!

01:43.937 --> 01:47.941
IF WISHES COULD KILL

02:02.622 --> 02:03.498
Se-ah.

02:05.375 --> 02:06.793
Se-ah.

02:09.045 --> 02:09.879
Yo, Se-ah.

02:12.382 --> 02:13.633
She's awake!

02:15.802 --> 02:16.886
Are you okay?

02:18.388 --> 02:19.764
Oh, thank God.

02:22.308 --> 02:25.353
Get away! Why'd you let her in here?

02:32.527 --> 02:34.070
I'm so sorry I upset you.

02:36.531 --> 02:39.284
I guess it'll take a while
to forgive everything I did.

02:46.958 --> 02:47.876
Se-ah.

02:48.960 --> 02:51.880
Do you remember anything?
After the warehouse?

02:54.507 --> 02:56.217
You know we all came back, right?

03:06.769 --> 03:09.689
So… what do you remember?

03:11.691 --> 03:13.193
Or where does it go blank?

03:14.611 --> 03:17.405
We got rid of the evil spirits,
so you can tell us. Their power's gone.

03:17.488 --> 03:19.616
There's a sort of gym?

03:21.201 --> 03:23.578
-With Coach?
-No.

03:24.078 --> 03:25.955
It's more of a storage thing.

03:26.039 --> 03:26.956
Lockers?

03:28.166 --> 03:29.250
There's a window.

03:30.084 --> 03:32.420
The warehouse where Hye-ryung
did her video?

03:33.922 --> 03:34.881
I'm sorry.

03:35.465 --> 03:37.425
I know that I started it
and put you through hell,

03:37.508 --> 03:41.763
and I… I know it's no excuse,
but I wasn't in control of my own actions.

03:42.472 --> 03:43.932
Please forgive me, Se-ah.

03:45.767 --> 03:48.228
What happened to the phone?
We found the red phone. Where is it?

03:48.311 --> 03:51.231
We were supposed to bring the phone
to Haetsal to get rid of the curse!

03:52.523 --> 03:55.026
Ha-joon! Did Bangwool get to the hospital?

03:55.109 --> 03:57.320
I remember he put himself
in front of that pole.

03:57.403 --> 03:59.280
-And it was really, really bad.
-Se-ah! Se-ah!

04:00.406 --> 04:01.491
-It's over.
-Huh?

04:02.116 --> 04:03.409
You got rid of the curse.

04:04.244 --> 04:05.161
I'll show you.

04:08.456 --> 04:11.334
The whole app is gone.
The timers all disappeared.

04:12.377 --> 04:13.711
Se-ah.

04:14.754 --> 04:17.298
-You were at my sister's compound.
-What?

04:19.092 --> 04:21.511
Girigo's not on anybody's phone.
Including yours.

04:23.972 --> 04:25.056
Really? What?

04:34.691 --> 04:35.525
Oh.

04:38.236 --> 04:39.445
So we're

04:40.697 --> 04:42.949
really done with all this?

04:45.201 --> 04:46.077
Mm-hmm.

04:53.668 --> 04:56.838
Have I been pushing you away a lot?

04:57.422 --> 04:59.173
More or less for a while, yeah.

05:05.763 --> 05:06.848
I'm sorry,

05:07.473 --> 05:08.391
Na-ri.

05:08.474 --> 05:10.393
Yeah, me too.

05:10.935 --> 05:12.645
I guess I deserved it.

05:13.604 --> 05:16.316
I just wish everything could go back
to the way it was.

05:37.545 --> 05:40.506
Guys. Who's got the next birthday?

05:41.090 --> 05:42.091
-Se-ah.
-Se-ah.

05:42.717 --> 05:43.885
Huh.

05:44.385 --> 05:47.638
Must be nice, Se-ah.
I bet neither of you knows mine.

05:48.139 --> 05:50.183
It's sometime later this year?

05:50.266 --> 05:52.727
-Wow!
-I don't know Ha-joon's either.

05:53.227 --> 05:55.355
Let's make a pact to forget his, okay?

05:55.438 --> 05:58.733
-When is it?
-Too late. You're not invited.

06:02.278 --> 06:05.323
MULTIMEDIA ROOM

06:08.659 --> 06:09.744
ASBESTOS REMOVAL
KEEP OUT

06:11.037 --> 06:12.121
ASBESTOS REMOVAL
KEEP OUT

06:13.873 --> 06:15.166
Se-ah, what's wrong?

06:16.209 --> 06:18.628
The bars that were on here.

06:19.128 --> 06:21.506
The work got done. They removed 'em.

06:21.589 --> 06:25.134
They finished construction.
Did you forget that too?

06:25.218 --> 06:28.304
The project they put on hold
before we started here

06:29.514 --> 06:31.557
is magically complete?

06:35.436 --> 06:36.729
I don't believe it.

07:39.625 --> 07:41.502
Hey! Is she okay?

07:42.044 --> 07:44.046
Se-ah?

07:53.848 --> 07:55.850
You need to bring Se-ah here now!
This is real!

07:56.476 --> 07:57.393
Geon-woo.

07:58.769 --> 07:59.812
I told you…

08:04.150 --> 08:06.903
…that you can't listen to her!

08:09.030 --> 08:10.114
Okay, I believe you.

08:13.326 --> 08:14.410
Se-ah.

08:14.911 --> 08:16.329
Sorry, sir, we'll get off here.

08:22.793 --> 08:25.004
So you're the one
who ran away from the curse.

08:26.130 --> 08:27.965
Track star.

08:28.799 --> 08:31.427
Na-ri, stop. I know this isn't you.

08:32.512 --> 08:35.890
You made a wish and it came true,
so now you die.

08:36.390 --> 08:38.017
Those are the rules.

08:55.159 --> 08:56.202
Hang on.

09:00.540 --> 09:03.209
I'll float a lantern up over the compound,
but you need to get moving.

09:04.961 --> 09:06.629
Se-ah. Hold on for me.

09:07.129 --> 09:08.839
I'm gonna find her. Huh?

09:35.241 --> 09:36.200
I got you.

09:40.162 --> 09:42.206
1 MINUTE, 50 M
BAEKUN-RO, SEORIN-SI

09:42.999 --> 09:43.916
Let's go.

10:02.310 --> 10:03.227
DESTINATION

10:03.311 --> 10:04.186
Oh!

10:12.028 --> 10:13.696
Where's the compound? Come on.

10:19.619 --> 10:20.620
Oh shit.

10:21.120 --> 10:23.372
Geon-woo.

10:47.855 --> 10:49.857
Just let yourself fall.
You're not gonna save her.

10:50.858 --> 10:52.568
The rules say she has to die.

11:07.667 --> 11:10.169
She's not dying! Fuck you.

11:10.670 --> 11:11.796
Fuck your rules!

11:15.424 --> 11:17.927
She's not dying out here.

11:18.010 --> 11:19.679
She's not dying!

11:34.985 --> 11:39.740
Se-ah, you saved my life.
I'm gonna get you out of this, I promise.

11:39.824 --> 11:42.284
We're gonna beat
this stupid curse together, okay?

11:49.542 --> 11:51.585
Hold on. We're almost there.

11:59.885 --> 12:01.053
Se-ah.

12:01.846 --> 12:04.306
You have to save…

12:04.932 --> 12:06.100
She has to live.

12:07.810 --> 12:09.019
Please, save her.

12:09.103 --> 12:10.438
I'm begging you.

12:41.594 --> 12:44.054
Cheonjiwang's bow and arrow
ordered the universe.

12:44.138 --> 12:45.765
Then Chilseong proclaimed

12:46.307 --> 12:50.269
that between the heavens and earth,
no evil spirits may torment humans.

13:28.140 --> 13:29.058
Why?

13:36.148 --> 13:37.149
That means

13:38.400 --> 13:40.319
the maehyung is still out there.

14:16.397 --> 14:17.940
Haetsal!

14:32.162 --> 14:33.080
I'm sorry.

14:34.874 --> 14:35.875
I failed.

14:37.585 --> 14:40.588
I used one of my arrows to destroy
the phone, but it didn't kill the curse.

14:43.382 --> 14:45.259
So, what do we have to do now?

14:57.813 --> 15:00.649
I've never faced
anything like this before so I'm not sure.

15:00.733 --> 15:03.694
All I know is the longer we stay here,
the more danger we're in.

15:04.486 --> 15:06.238
I think our only option
is to make a new door.

15:12.244 --> 15:13.120
Look!

15:17.750 --> 15:18.876
It's her.

15:20.544 --> 15:21.795
Hye-ryung.

15:27.259 --> 15:29.970
Did Do Hye-ryung get free of the curse?

15:34.016 --> 15:36.352
The girl pointed
to someone who was behind me.

15:36.977 --> 15:39.521
Why would ghosts
go out of their way to come here?

15:50.491 --> 15:52.785
The multimedia room.

15:58.082 --> 15:59.959
She's telling us it wasn't her.

16:01.627 --> 16:04.004
She's not the one who made Girigo.

16:05.965 --> 16:07.716
It was Kwon Si-won's idea.

16:13.639 --> 16:16.308
If Si-won is the one
who called the demon spirits,

16:16.392 --> 16:18.811
we have to get hold of the maehyung
she made to start all this.

16:19.979 --> 16:21.522
We need to find where she made her wish,

16:21.605 --> 16:23.857
but I have to leave
to get what we need to beat her.

16:23.941 --> 16:25.943
You're gonna leave me here by myself?

16:26.026 --> 16:28.362
Right now, we're no match
for Si-won in this space.

16:28.445 --> 16:31.240
I need to go back and create a deolmi,
or we don't stand a chance.

16:31.323 --> 16:34.702
I think Hye-ryung is trying to show you
where to find the red phone Si-won used.

16:34.785 --> 16:36.912
You need to go back in there,
and this time'll be it.

16:39.581 --> 16:42.126
This will offer you protection
until I get back.

16:42.209 --> 16:45.295
As long as it covers your face, they can't
detect you. I'm counting on you.

17:22.583 --> 17:23.751
Kwon Si-won!

17:24.543 --> 17:25.711
Si-won!

17:35.012 --> 17:36.930
What are you doing over there?

17:38.474 --> 17:39.349
Hye-ryung?

17:39.433 --> 17:40.684
Let's go.

17:49.818 --> 17:50.736
How…

18:21.225 --> 18:22.226
Where are you?

18:31.110 --> 18:32.444
Where are you?

18:37.699 --> 18:40.285
She was pointing in here.
Where else could it be?

18:41.495 --> 18:43.664
Let's go hang out and catch up, okay?

18:44.998 --> 18:45.874
Where?

18:46.708 --> 18:48.085
We're ghosts.

18:48.919 --> 18:50.420
We can go wherever we want.

18:51.004 --> 18:52.798
Not if we're bound to our wishes.

18:52.881 --> 18:54.383
Stay here then.

20:10.626 --> 20:11.627
By the way…

20:14.671 --> 20:15.505
Yeah?

20:42.866 --> 20:44.034
Se-ah.

20:49.498 --> 20:51.208
That incense smell on you.

20:54.795 --> 20:56.672
It's not from my mom's house.

21:28.453 --> 21:30.372
Na-ri.

21:31.581 --> 21:32.666
Is it really you in there?

21:36.211 --> 21:38.505
How come you're doing this?

21:38.588 --> 21:39.965
Eye for an eye.

21:41.049 --> 21:42.092
You think I forgot?

21:42.592 --> 21:44.136
How you guys

21:45.345 --> 21:47.597
tried to take me out
without a second thought?

21:48.807 --> 21:51.643
No, Na-ri. It… it wasn't like that.

21:52.144 --> 21:53.979
You made it so we had no choice.

21:54.646 --> 21:55.939
Geon-woo had to--

21:59.234 --> 22:00.110
Stop!

22:05.657 --> 22:07.909
Na-ri. Listen.

22:16.543 --> 22:18.128
You had no choice?

22:20.088 --> 22:23.050
Sure. Always your lame excuse.

22:23.633 --> 22:24.968
Pretending you had no choice

22:25.552 --> 22:28.347
so you could look like the good girl
who protects everyone.

22:29.139 --> 22:31.433
You say we're your best friends,
but you keep lying to us.

22:33.143 --> 22:36.355
You knew I had a massive crush on Geon-woo
and you went behind my back.

22:37.022 --> 22:39.191
And then you lied
about not being together.

22:40.859 --> 22:42.027
Was that fun for you?

22:42.110 --> 22:43.153
Me and him…

22:44.821 --> 22:47.491
We only liked each other as friends.
I was gonna tell you when we--

22:47.574 --> 22:48.867
Liar!

22:50.577 --> 22:52.871
Enough of your "I was gonna" bullshit.

23:00.253 --> 23:01.713
Backstabbing bitch.

23:07.427 --> 23:08.887
Caught ya.

23:12.474 --> 23:14.351
Running around my space like you own it.

24:17.497 --> 24:19.624
Just die!

24:28.758 --> 24:29.593
Agh!

24:34.347 --> 24:37.517
Na-ri, we can fix this!
You didn't know what you were doing.

24:37.601 --> 24:39.102
Hyeong-wook, Geon-woo, you.

24:44.691 --> 24:47.444
You didn't mean for anyone to die.
It was a mistake!

24:47.944 --> 24:49.696
It's the app that took over.

25:16.598 --> 25:17.724
I do…

25:19.392 --> 25:20.810
want all of you dead.

25:21.436 --> 25:22.687
Hyeong-wook started it.

25:24.564 --> 25:26.191
It's not fair.

25:26.274 --> 25:29.528
If that loser hadn't told me it existed,

25:29.611 --> 25:31.863
I never even
would have made a wish on Girigo,

25:31.947 --> 25:34.157
and I wouldn't be so fucking miserable!

26:29.796 --> 26:33.049
What did you say? It's not fair?

27:48.083 --> 27:50.669
FEBRUARY 1, 2005
KWON SI-WON

27:50.752 --> 27:51.961
Kwon Si-won.

28:12.982 --> 28:14.150
Si-won?

28:21.658 --> 28:23.451
I think enough people have suffered.

28:23.952 --> 28:25.912
You're getting your wish.

28:25.995 --> 28:28.373
So go away!

28:51.479 --> 28:54.357
It isn't the arrow.

28:54.858 --> 28:58.903
I became a deolmi,
since nothing else would be enough.

29:01.614 --> 29:04.159
And the more my blood soaks in the thread,

29:05.452 --> 29:08.037
the more I control you.

29:28.349 --> 29:31.686
GIRIGO
MAKE A WISH

29:31.770 --> 29:32.645
Finally.

29:49.704 --> 29:50.830
Haetsal!

29:59.547 --> 30:01.299
GIRIGO
MAKE A WISH

30:13.686 --> 30:15.313
Se-ah!

31:08.950 --> 31:10.326
Se-ah?

31:10.910 --> 31:12.412
Se-ah?

31:12.495 --> 31:13.454
Se-ah!

31:20.795 --> 31:21.796
Did we

31:23.089 --> 31:24.465
end the curse?

31:26.843 --> 31:27.886
Yes.

31:29.846 --> 31:31.514
It's over. The curse is gone.

31:54.078 --> 31:55.872
Goddamn.

31:56.456 --> 31:59.626
They really mean it
when they say apps are hard to get rid of.

32:29.989 --> 32:34.619
You made it. Today,
we're wrapping up a really tough semester.

32:36.537 --> 32:39.457
We've been through a lot of hardships
together, haven't we?

32:40.792 --> 32:42.919
Many no one could have imagined.

32:43.419 --> 32:46.005
And I know it weighs heavily
on all of you.

32:46.589 --> 32:47.840
As it does on me.

32:47.924 --> 32:52.845
Some of you lost some very close friends.
That is a pain that only time can heal…

32:53.680 --> 32:54.722
Promise.

33:56.159 --> 33:57.326
Hyeong-wook,

33:58.411 --> 33:59.746
go in harmony.

34:00.413 --> 34:04.083
May you find peace in the place
where there is no troubles and no sorrows.

34:04.167 --> 34:05.877
Go content and joyous.

35:02.058 --> 35:04.227
Girigo? Why's it still on your phone?

35:09.565 --> 35:12.151
Are you scared you'll forget Hyeong-wook
if you delete it?

35:12.777 --> 35:13.694
Mm-hmm.

35:17.490 --> 35:19.075
And because of the guilt.

35:20.368 --> 35:24.288
Na-ri would still be with us
if only I'd been strong enough.

35:26.040 --> 35:28.793
Don't. You were incredibly brave.

35:30.586 --> 35:32.130
You did everything you could.

35:49.188 --> 35:52.859
GIRIGO
WOULD YOU LIKE TO DELETE THIS APP?

35:53.568 --> 35:54.652
GIRIGO HAS BEEN DELETED

36:02.285 --> 36:04.120
So as I get to the door,

36:04.620 --> 36:07.290
I feel a piercing "thunk,"
and I can't move anymore.

36:07.373 --> 36:08.332
Pinned me to the car.

36:08.833 --> 36:12.795
I am in this half-standing, half-sitting
position, and blood is everywhere,

36:12.879 --> 36:16.048
and I'm trying not to pass out
'cause it went right through me.

36:16.132 --> 36:19.760
So I'm thinking,
"Wow, this is how I'm gonna die?"

36:19.844 --> 36:21.762
And then I start to feel much lighter.

36:22.263 --> 36:23.139
And I'm

36:23.848 --> 36:27.185
holding on to an envoy from the underworld
crossing the Samdocheon.

36:27.268 --> 36:31.189
And I'm nearly to the other side
when this piercing, desperate voice calls.

36:31.272 --> 36:33.733
"Bangwool! Brother-in-law!"

36:33.816 --> 36:37.737
I mean, he's just bawling. It was so loud,
the whole underworld could hear it!

36:37.820 --> 36:39.280
What? I didn't cry!

36:41.449 --> 36:42.491
Please don't die.

36:42.575 --> 36:44.535
Right. You were just cutting onions.

36:45.536 --> 36:46.412
Sure.

36:48.206 --> 36:51.417
I came back so I could tell Haetsal
her brother finally caved.

36:59.258 --> 37:01.010
And to give her the gift I picked up.

37:01.636 --> 37:05.556
I saw Hyeong-wook at the ceremony,
by the way. Looking very happy.

37:08.768 --> 37:10.144
That's not the only thing I saw.

37:11.145 --> 37:13.064
I saw the power that resides in you.

37:14.106 --> 37:15.900
The way it moves and flows.

37:19.195 --> 37:20.029
What?

37:20.112 --> 37:23.407
Wait. You're talking about
what you told me at the hospital?

37:23.908 --> 37:26.327
-About being able to see spirits?
-Mm.

37:28.663 --> 37:29.538
Haetsal.

37:33.084 --> 37:33.918
Uh…

37:37.463 --> 37:39.298
My new power survived the curse.

37:42.051 --> 37:44.387
I think I have a way
for you to leave the compound.

39:42.129 --> 39:44.673
WHY DO YOU THINK CHOI HYEONG-WOOK DIED?

39:56.560 --> 39:59.522
WELL… I'LL TELL YOU
ONCE YOU BRING ME THE PHONE. LOL

39:59.605 --> 40:00.564
DID YOU FIND IT?

40:00.648 --> 40:02.858
I FOUND IT! IT REALLY WAS STILL THERE!

40:05.069 --> 40:07.363
050201 IS TYPING…

40:07.446 --> 40:09.281
SEE? WHAT DID I TELL YOU? LOL

40:17.039 --> 40:18.791
GIRIGO
